# Runtime user data (NEVER commit — zero data/token in repo).
# 运行期数据在 $APPDATA/Sinan(仓库外),这里只按文件类型忽略,
# 绝不用 cache//logs//models/ 这类目录名(会误伤同名源码包:
# services/engine/sinan/cache、apps/desktop/src/pages/logs 等)。
*.db
*.db-wal
*.db-shm
*.duckdb
*.parquet
*.log
# 若把 SINAN_DATA_DIR 指到仓库内,请用此约定目录(已忽略)
/.sinan-data/

# Secrets — red line: never commit any token/credential
*.token
.env
.env.*
secrets.*

